                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════ CTA ════════ -->
    <section class="final-cta">
        <div class="narrow">
            <div class="cta-inner reveal">
                <h2 class="cta-h2">The future of attendance<br>isn't a checklist.<br><span class="accent-text">It's a camera.</span></h2>
                <div class="cta-row">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Daivik1520/facial_recognition" target="_blank" class="btn-fill">Explore on GitHub ↗</a>
                    <a href="tel:+917995456600" class="btn-line">Get in Touch →</a>
